{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/how-to-use-figma/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2>설치</h2>\n<p>피그마는 웹 기반 브라우저이지만, 계속 사용할 예정이라면 데스크탑 앱으로 다운해서 사용하는 것을 추천!</p>\n<br>\n<h2>기본적인 사용법</h2>\n<h3>🧑🏻‍💻 개발자 관점</h3>\n<p>디자인된 피그마 파일을 보고 프론트엔드 개발자가 활용할 수 있는 방법들!</p>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>기능</strong></summary>\n<div markdown=\"1\">\n<h3>1. <strong>요소의 CSS 속성 참고하기</strong></h3>\n<p>원하는 요소를 선택하고 <code class=\"language-text\">Inspect</code> 탭에서 CSS 코드를 확인할 수 있다. 상황에 맞게 수정해야하는 경우도 분명 존재하기 때문에 이 코드를 전부 그대로 사용하는 것은 추천하지 않는다.</p>\n<div style=\"width: 40%; padding: 1rem 0;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 478px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/1282f15ee961aff13f9fb6fde77c72ca/e4b77/css.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 114.0625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/1282f15ee961aff13f9fb6fde77c72ca/a59e9/css.webp 192w,\n/static/1282f15ee961aff13f9fb6fde77c72ca/0ca9f/css.webp 384w,\n/static/1282f15ee961aff13f9fb6fde77c72ca/3c317/css.webp 478w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/1282f15ee961aff13f9fb6fde77c72ca/3b721/css.png 192w,\n/static/1282f15ee961aff13f9fb6fde77c72ca/66595/css.png 384w,\n/static/1282f15ee961aff13f9fb6fde77c72ca/e4b77/css.png 478w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/1282f15ee961aff13f9fb6fde77c72ca/e4b77/css.png\" alt=\"css\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n<h3>2. <strong>사용된 이미지 저장하기</strong></h3>\n<p>원하는 이미지를 선택해서 원하는 포맷과 배율로 <code class=\"language-text\">export</code>할 수 있다. 전체 이미지를 <code class=\"language-text\">export</code>하고 싶다면 <code class=\"language-text\">file > export</code>를 클릭하여 전체 이미지를 저장할 수 있다.</p>\n<div style=\"width: 40%; padding: 1rem 0;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 478px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/bb83c556b95de78a166ab85d494a623c/e4b77/export.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 79.16666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/bb83c556b95de78a166ab85d494a623c/a59e9/export.webp 192w,\n/static/bb83c556b95de78a166ab85d494a623c/0ca9f/export.webp 384w,\n/static/bb83c556b95de78a166ab85d494a623c/3c317/export.webp 478w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/bb83c556b95de78a166ab85d494a623c/3b721/export.png 192w,\n/static/bb83c556b95de78a166ab85d494a623c/66595/export.png 384w,\n/static/bb83c556b95de78a166ab85d494a623c/e4b77/export.png 478w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/bb83c556b95de78a166ab85d494a623c/e4b77/export.png\" alt=\"export\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n<h3>3. <strong>코멘트를 활용해서 소통하기</strong></h3>\n<p>원하는 위치에 코멘트를 작성할 수 있다. 작성 후 해결이 완료된 코멘트는 체크 버튼을 클릭하여 닫을 수 있다. 혹시 나중에 해결된 코멘트도 보고 싶다면 아래의 설정에서 <code class=\"language-text\">show resolved comments</code>를 선택하면 된다.</p>\n<div style=\"width: 40%; padding: 1rem 0;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 478px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/7b8fcaeb1546e1c613c09c7b1d95a6c4/e4b77/comment.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 98.95833333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/7b8fcaeb1546e1c613c09c7b1d95a6c4/a59e9/comment.webp 192w,\n/static/7b8fcaeb1546e1c613c09c7b1d95a6c4/0ca9f/comment.webp 384w,\n/static/7b8fcaeb1546e1c613c09c7b1d95a6c4/3c317/comment.webp 478w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/7b8fcaeb1546e1c613c09c7b1d95a6c4/3b721/comment.png 192w,\n/static/7b8fcaeb1546e1c613c09c7b1d95a6c4/66595/comment.png 384w,\n/static/7b8fcaeb1546e1c613c09c7b1d95a6c4/e4b77/comment.png 478w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/7b8fcaeb1546e1c613c09c7b1d95a6c4/e4b77/comment.png\" alt=\"comment\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</details>\n<br>\n<h3>🎨 디자이너 관점</h3>\n<p>피그마를 사용해서 실제 디자인을 해야할 때 기본적으로 알면 좋은 것들!</p>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>디자인</strong></summary>\n<div markdown=\"1\">\n<h3>1. 기본적인 UI 만들기</h3>\n<p>기본 도구를 이용하여 간단한 버튼, 텍스트, 아이콘 등을 만들 수 있다. 특히, 펜 툴을 사용하여 좀 더 정밀하고 원하는 모양을 만들 수 있다.</p>\n<div style=\"width: 45%; padding: 1rem 0;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/f13b2f5fb3e248685bd6c65c07c6fcd6/efd7b/ui.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 30.729166666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/f13b2f5fb3e248685bd6c65c07c6fcd6/a59e9/ui.webp 192w,\n/static/f13b2f5fb3e248685bd6c65c07c6fcd6/0ca9f/ui.webp 384w,\n/static/f13b2f5fb3e248685bd6c65c07c6fcd6/7df04/ui.webp 760w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/f13b2f5fb3e248685bd6c65c07c6fcd6/3b721/ui.png 192w,\n/static/f13b2f5fb3e248685bd6c65c07c6fcd6/66595/ui.png 384w,\n/static/f13b2f5fb3e248685bd6c65c07c6fcd6/efd7b/ui.png 760w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/f13b2f5fb3e248685bd6c65c07c6fcd6/efd7b/ui.png\" alt=\"ui\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n<h3>2. <strong>컴포넌트로 만들어서 재사용성 높이기</strong></h3>\n<p>반복되는 요소를 컴포넌트로 만들자. 그럼 하나씩 다 복붙할 필요가 없고 간격도 하나하나 조정할 필요가 없다.</p>\n<div style=\"width: 45%; padding: 1rem 0;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/4c573/component.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 68.22916666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/a59e9/component.webp 192w,\n/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/0ca9f/component.webp 384w,\n/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/dc9b9/component.webp 768w,\n/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/e2c2f/component.webp 1152w,\n/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/bdb72/component.webp 1300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/3b721/component.png 192w,\n/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/66595/component.png 384w,\n/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/fe486/component.png 768w,\n/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/d2d74/component.png 1152w,\n/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/4c573/component.png 1300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/f117038f706f4b2eabf2f7b0b68b038b/fe486/component.png\" alt=\"component\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n<h3>3. 픽셀에서 벡터로 변환하여 원하는대로 디자인하기</h3>\n<p>일러스트레이터와 기능이 유사하다. 보통 로고를 만들거나, 아이콘을 만들 때 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<div style=\"width: 45%; padding: 1rem 0;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 762px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/254162e3d0c35d34aa51ffa2e5c25d93/98085/text.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.77083333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/254162e3d0c35d34aa51ffa2e5c25d93/a59e9/text.webp 192w,\n/static/254162e3d0c35d34aa51ffa2e5c25d93/0ca9f/text.webp 384w,\n/static/254162e3d0c35d34aa51ffa2e5c25d93/d8efd/text.webp 762w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 762px) 100vw, 762px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/254162e3d0c35d34aa51ffa2e5c25d93/3b721/text.png 192w,\n/static/254162e3d0c35d34aa51ffa2e5c25d93/66595/text.png 384w,\n/static/254162e3d0c35d34aa51ffa2e5c25d93/98085/text.png 762w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 762px) 100vw, 762px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/254162e3d0c35d34aa51ffa2e5c25d93/98085/text.png\" alt=\"text\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n텍스트\n<div style=\"width: 45%; padding: 1rem 0;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/51f47/flatten.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 57.8125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/a59e9/flatten.webp 192w,\n/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/0ca9f/flatten.webp 384w,\n/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/dc9b9/flatten.webp 768w,\n/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/0ad40/flatten.webp 892w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/3b721/flatten.png 192w,\n/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/66595/flatten.png 384w,\n/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/fe486/flatten.png 768w,\n/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/51f47/flatten.png 892w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/c9d8b5d8bcd1e5a15954ce24d7de66eb/fe486/flatten.png\" alt=\"flatten\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n텍스트 → 벡터화 (flatten or outline stroke)\n<div style=\"width: 45%; padding: 1rem 0;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/1dbb4/complete.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 58.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/a59e9/complete.webp 192w,\n/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/0ca9f/complete.webp 384w,\n/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/dc9b9/complete.webp 768w,\n/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/2c16e/complete.webp 852w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/3b721/complete.png 192w,\n/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/66595/complete.png 384w,\n/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/fe486/complete.png 768w,\n/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/1dbb4/complete.png 852w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/b0e4583b21a83dca79c49a88a07e2209/fe486/complete.png\" alt=\"complete\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n변형 후 완성\n</div>\n<br>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>프로토타입</strong></summary>\n<div markdown=\"1\">\n  모든 페이지 디자인이 끝나면 이제 프로토타입을 만든다. 프로토타입은 실제 개발이 되었을 때와 같이 미리 서비스를 확인해보며 사용성 측면에서 테스트 해볼 수 있게 해준다.\n  보통 원하는 요소를 클릭했을 때 다음 페이지로 이동되도록 요소 - 페이지 연결을 해준다. 피그마에서는 클릭 이벤트 뿐 아니라 여러가지 다양한 이벤트를 제공하기 때문에 원하는 요소에 원하는 이벤트를 연결해주면 된다. 또, 화면 전환 방식 애니메이션도 선택이 가능하다.\n<div style=\"width: 95%; padding: 1rem 0; margin: 0 auto;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/6482f/prototype.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 59.375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/a59e9/prototype.webp 192w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/0ca9f/prototype.webp 384w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/dc9b9/prototype.webp 768w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/e2c2f/prototype.webp 1152w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/f3efb/prototype.webp 1536w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/f3963/prototype.webp 2500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/3b721/prototype.png 192w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/66595/prototype.png 384w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/fe486/prototype.png 768w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/d2d74/prototype.png 1152w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/e8464/prototype.png 1536w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/6482f/prototype.png 2500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/fe486/prototype.png\" alt=\"prototype\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n  <br>\n  <aside>\n    💡 <strong>요즘 자주 사용되는 레이아웃인 가로 스크롤 만들기</strong>\n        <br>컴포넌트를 만들고 그 안에 인스턴스를 원하는 만큼 만든다. 컴포넌트 가로 세로 영역을 잡아주고 prototypes 탭에 들어간다. 거기서 overflow scorlling을 horizontal로 설정해주면 끝!\n  </aside>\n</div>\n</details>\n</details>\n<br>\n<h3>📌 자주 쓰는 단축어</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">command + 마우스 휠(+/-)</code>: 화면 확대 축소</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">shift + 크기 조절</code>: 이미지 비율 유지하면서 확대 축소</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">option</code>: 요소에 마우스 hover 한 상태이면, 그 요소를 기준으로 몇 픽셀만큼 떨어져 있는지 수치가 나옴</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">option</code>: 요소 복사 붙여넣기 한번에 가능</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">shift + option</code>: 복사 붙여넣기인데, 가로 혹은 세로 라인 유지 가능</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">command + [/]</code>: 요소 뒤/앞으로 보내기</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h3>References</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Figma</a></li>\n</ul>\n<br>","frontmatter":{"title":"피그마 간단 사용법","summary":"홈페이지를 운영하는 많은 사람들 또는 기업들이 검색 페이지 최상단에 보여지게 하기 위해 어떤 최적화 작업을 하는지 알아보자.","date":"2023.01.02","categories":{"type":["블로그"],"tags":["Figma","Design"]},"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/52576/prototype.png","srcSet":"/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/40878/prototype.png 625w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/b027c/prototype.png 1250w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/52576/prototype.png 2500w","sizes":"(min-width: 2500px) 2500px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/ce6b4/prototype.webp 625w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/7b59a/prototype.webp 1250w,\n/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/bbb7a/prototype.webp 2500w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 2500px) 2500px, 100vw"}]},"width":2500,"height":1484}},"publicURL":"/static/65d78c984eeeeeeda3e14cd04a5ab680/prototype.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/how-to-use-figma/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}